    "name": "todoke-route",
    "purpose": "last-mile stop sequencing (NN + 2-opt) + SAE-L4 sidewalk ODD safety envelope (G7) + R1 curb-to-door rover sim (kinematic stand-in for kami-autodrive); 13 tests green (7 route + 6 sim) + curb_to_door example; sequencer mirrored by methods/last_mile.py (parity-tested)"
  },
